description:
No more clothing distractions on your ascents. Ideal for strategic approaches and all-day hikes, the R1 Pullover is long on warmth and short on weight. Power Grid fabric wicks moisture and breathes well for comfort on long hikes. When you reach for a hold or a tent pole, the fabric stretches with you. Alpine-specific features include a balaclava hood that layers under a helmet and a long hem that stays tucked under your harness.Polartec® Power Grid® fabric with Polygiene® permanent odour control is light and breathable with outstanding stretch and durability.Pullover silhouette with deep center-front zipper for easy on/off and venting options.Chest pocket has slim zip install, zipper garage and mesh pocket bag.Sleeves have on-seam thumbholes for extra coverage in chilly weather.

